Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What complete fools you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this the Millennium Puzzle is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a Dark Game.... I'll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,136)}Trap of the Metamorph Plot! Flame Swordsman in Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a duelist of the Dark Games, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura? I'm not Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... you should know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever gets all the Millennium Items will have everything he wants from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll bring back everyone's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I win, I'll take your Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is Commander in defense mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's souls were...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,transferred to the card they like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to realize that now... And now, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this duel, the soul card that loses, just like the other cards, goes to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the God of Death will get to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Commander is taken by the God of Death, Honda's body will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz10\pos(339,115)}"Hiroto Honda"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally got it. But the Dark Game can't be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn! What will you do, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely save you from the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play everyone's soul card carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... to defeat the White Thief now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there's no other card than Jounouchi-kun's Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are... Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be calm and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is now sealed inside the card of the Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't win the duel, you can't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're defeated in battle, you will go to the graveyard, like Honda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, to stop this dangerous duel, and to get everyone back safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Leave it to me! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a dream, isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with! So, who's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura's the enemy? I don't get this dream one damn bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not Bakura-kun. He is using Bakura-kun's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dark Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all... but let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter, the enemy is weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metamorph Pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Did I do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Metamorph Pot appears, our entire hand must go to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this moment, it's a good thing that I have no cards with the guys' souls, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician is the card that has Yugi's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another set one? To have the card with Yugi's soul in my hand would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also a Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead, to revive Honda-kun! {Shisha Sosei}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too? What is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we were transformed into Monster Cards from Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I really don't understand it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Yugi... Aren't you up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to keep secrets. We have to fight with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yugi is the spirit of a "Yugi" that sleeps within the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for not telling you about this until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not my intention to hide this from everyone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... Yugi is Yugi! And we are friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way... where's Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must still be in the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with before Anzu shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's hurry and end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment! This turn is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metamorph Pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to discard our hands again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same card as the previous one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Anzu's soul card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you draw a good card?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're allowed up to 3 of the same card in a deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still one Metamorph Pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Metamorph Pot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Just Desserts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For each monster you have in the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it inflicts 500 damage points directly to your Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but one more attack, and I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this keeps up, I'll lose, and everyone's lives will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he uses another Metamorph Pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keeping Anzu's soul card in my hand is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone cosplaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Shh! Don't speak too loud! That weird Bakura will notice you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we are in the Duel Monsters world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Bakura-kun is being controlled by a Duelist of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's two Yugis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it, but to put it simple, there's a cool Yugi and a normal Yugi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll show you that I can be cool too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat the hidden enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body... is paralyzed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the monster that attacks the Electrical Lizard isn't an electric type,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't attack in the next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to hide is useless.... that's Anzu, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Flesh-Eating Insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... what's that card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that card is activated, one monster on the field is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us will, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go back to that graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's so powerful, we just have to defeat it in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the card's attacked, it activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! There isn't a way to prevent it from activating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the Trap Card... Hunting Horn of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So that's a trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, to activate it, it requires a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if the Flesh-Eating Insect is activated, who knows which of us it will destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just came back from the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jounouchi-kun!\N- Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Yugi! This is your chance! Use me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I don't want my friends to be sacrificed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the trap card Hunting Horn of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice one monster on the field to activate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your monster's effect is negated and it is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jounouchi-kun!\N Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I leave the rest up to you... Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you will all go to the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll just die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu's body is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Saint Magician is activated...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can recover one magic card from my graveyard and add it to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jounouchi!\N- Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them being in the graveyard is weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friendship between the four of us will create a miracle... definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you that this bond between you will not last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bakura-kun's favorite card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this card's power on Black Magician Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will obey me as if you were mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will fight your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how low will this guy fall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want! With this, your friendship ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all die in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun's soul was also sealed inside a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun... now... attack me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...Hurry up and attack me to defeat the Duelist of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if I do that... Your soul will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! That's better than having an evil being controlling my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Black Magician Yugi, attack the High Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Just a little more and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Millennium Ring is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is an archaeologist that travels around the world, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he went to Egypt, he found and bought the Millennium Ring and a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who sold the Ring and the card to my father said he was from the Dark World.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a long dream I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A terrifying Dark Bakura was in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- Don't scare us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way.... there were two Yugis... that was really a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running to see what happened, we find Mai Kujaku-san who lost all her Star chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to retrieve her star chips, Yugi duels with the Dark Player Killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want him to bet his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Yugi! How will you fight if you can't see what is hiding in the darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: A Duel of Darkness! The Castle that Disappears Into the Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
